title: Teemo Bug
body: In a Normal game of summoners rift the cottontail Teemo on my team made the sound effects of blitzcranks speed boost whenever he used move quick.

replies.body:
Hey DJ Mikasa, 

Thanks for the report! We'll look into this issue and get this resolved ASAP.

**EDIT:** While similar in sound, Cottontail Teemo is playing his intended Move Quick (W) SFX.
